flowchart TD
    %% Clear Server Search Bar - Flow Chart

    A([User types in search input]) --> B[ServerSearch component renders]
    B --> C{searchQuery.length > 0?}

    C -->|No| D[Return null - hide results]
    C -->|Yes| E[Get servers from AppContext]

    E --> F[Filter by user membership]
    F --> G[Filter by name match]
    G --> H{filteredServers.length > 0?}

    H -->|Yes| I[Display server list]
    H -->|No| J[Display 'No spaces found']

    I --> K{User selects server?}
    J --> L{User clears search?}

    K -->|Yes| M[Set selected server, clear channel/DM]
    K -->|No| N{User modifies query?}

    N -->|Yes| C
    N -->|No| K

    L -->|Yes| D
    L -->|No| J

    M --> O([Navigation complete])
    D --> P([Search idle])
